　　月　　4 　　日\r\n                            書記官　黃怡禎","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CYDV/111%2c%e9%87%8d%e8%a8%b4%2c14%2c20221004%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CYDV,111,重訴,14,20221004,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"重訴","JNO":"14","JDATE":"20221004","JTITLE":"拆屋還地"}